Buttons, Alerts, Badges, and Tags
Primary Button: Blue background with white text.
Secondary Button: Green background with white text.
Success Alert: Green background with dark text.
Error Alert: Red-toned background for warnings.
Verified Badge: Green icon or label indicating trusted seller.
Feature Tag: Blue label highlighting promoted sellers or products.


2. Typography Pairing
Headings Font: Poppins – modern, geometric, strong presence.
Body Font: Inter – clean, readable for interfaces.
Fallback Fonts: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif.
Hierarchy:
H1 – Bold, large for hero titles.
H2 – Section headings.
Body – Standard paragraph text for readability.


3. Homepage Wireframe Overview
Header: Logo on the left, navigation links on the right, primary CTA button.
Hero Section: Bold headline, short description, search bar, and featured CTA.
Featured Sellers: Grid layout displaying verified sellers with badges.
Product Highlights: Cards with images, prices, and contact buttons.
Trust Section: Explanation of seller verification and safety.
Footer: Links, social media, and contact information.